title: Golden retrievers are a large dog breed with soft, luxurious fur and charming eyes.
description: With a life expectancy ranging from 10 to 12 years, they come in various coat colors including golden, light golden, and dark golden. Males typically weigh between 30 to 34 kilograms, while females weigh slightly less, ranging from 24 to 29 kilograms.
